name: Alien Street Photography 👽📸
description:
As part of Genuary 2022, the prompt of "Space" gave the inspiration for creating a series of 4 works based on alien environments, flora, and lighting.

Using VQGAN, I prompted the computer with information to search for such as glitch, downtown, city, sci-fi, futuristic, and alleyways.
